营投票反对。 据美媒报道，该法案除了包括对以色列 143 亿美元军事援助外，还将削减针对美国国税局的预算。众议院共和党人和民主党人均支持向以色列提供援助，但共和党人在该法案中加入削减政府预算的做法遭到民主党人强烈不满。 接下来，该法案将交由参议院审议。参议院多数党领袖、民主党人舒默当天表示，该法案在参议院不可能获得通过，共和党人的做法只会推迟以色列获得援助的时间。美众议院批准向以色列提供 143 亿美元军事援助 - 中新网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9fd98865e1620666e10795785ec2f484_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.8 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/628925424"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhIiqwJmS3P94EAMaCTEwMjAzOTg4NiCU0JGqBjAAOIoDQBhyCTYyODkyNTQyNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1699067308.647954", "card_id": "Q_627863871", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 357}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "当你老了，你想要过怎样的生活？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我应该会回老家，过一个乡村生活和我的另一半，希望能平平淡淡的度过下半生。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.8 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/627863871"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhIiqwJmS3P94EAMaCTEwMTgwNDIyMSCh9eapBjAAOK0DQBlyCTYyNzg2Mzg3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1699067308.648287", "card_id": "Q_628367427", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "可以一稿多投然后哪边中了把其余的撤稿吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.8 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/628367427"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhIiqwJmS3P94EAMaCTEwMTkxNTgzNiCUg/2pBjAAOC9AGnIJNjI4MzY3NDI3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27